---
import BaseLayout from '../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import t from '../../../i18n/pt.json';
const lang = 'pt';
---
<BaseLayout lang={lang} t={t} title={`${t.terms.title} | SELLUM`} description={t.site.description}>
<article class="max-w-container-max mx-auto px-margin-mobile md:px-margin-desktop py-stack-xl" style="max-width:720px">
<h1 class="font-headline-lg text-headline-lg text-primary mb-stack-md">{t.terms.title}</h1>
<p class="text-secondary font-body-md mb-6">{t.terms.updated}</p>
<div class="space-y-6 text-secondary font-body-md leading-relaxed">
<p>Ao acessar ou usar nosso site e serviços, você concorda com estes Termos de Serviço.</p>
<h2 class="font-headline-lg text-[24px] text-primary mt-8 mb-4">Licença de Uso</h2><p>Permissão concedida para acesso temporário aos materiais do site para uso pessoal e não comercial.</p>
<h2 class="font-headline-lg text-[24px] text-primary mt-8 mb-4">Contato</h2><p><a href="mailto:info@sellumlabs.com" class="text-primary underline">info@sellumlabs.com</a></p>
</div>
</article>
</BaseLayout>
